<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="date=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="address=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="email=no">
    <title>Payment Setup Confirmation - {{quoteReference}}</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <noscript>
        <xml>
            <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
                <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
            </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
    <style type="text/css">
{{> shared-email-styles}}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            {{> email-header-logo}}
            <h1>Payment Setup Confirmed</h1>
            <p>Quote #{{quoteReference}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{customerName}},</div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                Your payment method has been successfully set up. Your booking is now confirmed and we'll automatically charge your payment method closer to your moving date.
            </div>
            
            <div class="payment-details">
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Quote Reference:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">#{{quoteReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value amount">£{{totalAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Amount Charged Today:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">£{{amountChargedToday}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if paymentDueDate}}
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Payment Due Date:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">{{paymentDueDate}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Payment Status:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value" style="color: #5aa5b3; font-weight: bold;">Payment Setup</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Setup Date:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">{{setupDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-notice">
                <h3>Payment Method Saved</h3>
                <p>Your payment method has been securely saved. We'll automatically charge it closer to your moving date. No further action is required from you.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Your booking is now confirmed and secured</li>
                    <li>Our team will contact you to finalize moving details</li>
                    <li>You'll receive updates about your booking via email</li>
                    <li>We'll automatically charge your payment method closer to your moving date</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="main-text">
                <p><strong>Need help?</strong> If you have any questions about your payment setup or booking, please contact our support team at support@tranzrmoves.com or call us at 0303 330 1101.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="transactional-note">
                <p>You received this email because you set up a payment method for quote #{{quoteReference}}. If you have any concerns about this email, please contact us at support@tranzrmoves.com.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{> email-footer-html}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>